<HEADLINE>
<P>
IS IT JUST AN X WITH ANOTHER NAME? READERS SOUND OFF ON THE NEW NC-17 MOVIE 
RATING; 
</P>
<P>
THE RECENT CHANGE IN THE MOVIE RATING SYSTEM PRODUCED A NUMBER OF RESPONSES. 
HERE ARE SOME. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A wolf in sheep's clothing is still a wolf. An X-rated movie with an NC-17 
rating is still an X-rated movie. 
</P>
<P>
I respectfully ask you to not advertise NC-17 movies. 
</P>
<P>
Otherwise, our family will be forced to get our news elsewhere. 
</P>
<P>
LINDA MURRAY, Sun Valley 
</P>
</TEXT>
