CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; BALLOTS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; SPECIAL INTEREST GROUPS; 
POLITICAL ENDORSEMENTS; CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS; CALIFORNIA -- CONSTITUTIONS; 
PROPOSITION 136 (SPECIAL TAX VOTE) 
</P>
