<P>
GROSSMONT AT LAST BEATS GOLDEN WEST IN VOLLEYBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Grossmont College defeated Golden West in a women's volleyball match Saturday 
after failing against the Rustlers (12-1) three times this season. 
</P>
<P>
Grossmont won, 11-15, 15-7, 15-10, 10-15, 15-9 in a nonconference match at 
Grossmont and improved to 9-4. Brenda Irby had 18 kills for Golden West. 
</P>
