<P>
A PERSONAL CHECK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Because I do rely upon your movie-rating system, I was confused and 
disappointed by your having given a single check ("Desperation Time") to the 
worthy film "The Seventh Sign" (Oct. 3, Channel 5). Aside from a miscast Jesus 
(Christ) and a penchant for some obviousness, I found the movie to meaningfully 
bring together biblical prophecy with current events, and to portray what a 
personal act of faith would be, in a rather inspiring way. 
</P>
<P>
Barry Klein, Los Angeles 
